oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Red Foley and the Dawnbusters - WLS Quick Elastic program - 1946-02-17 - Part 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WLS program featuring Red Foley and the Dawnbusters, sponsored by Quick Elastic starch. Originally broadcast 1946-02-17, part 1. The Dawnbusters includes Dave Bohme (fiddle).
